%1$s still awaiting your vote. Each has a %2$d-day voting window from when it was confirmed.'=>'这是您今天的应用摘要，关于 %1$s 的申请仍在等待您的投票。每个申请自确认起都有 %2$d 天的投票期。','Prefer these one at a time again? You can switch back any time from your notification preferences link below.'=>'更愿意一次只看一个吗？您可以随时通过下面的通知偏好链接切换回来。','Vote in favor of this application?'=>'要赞成此申请吗？','Vote against this application?'=>'要反对此申请吗？','You voted in favor of this application.'=>'您已投赞成票。','You voted against this application.'=>'您已投反对票。','%d positive vote recorded so far.'=>'目前已记录 %d 票赞成。','is active and configured for'=>'已激活并为以下内容配置','Subdomain'=>'子域名','routing mode'=>'路由模式','This conflicts with Agnosis artist subdomains — both plugins would claim the same subdomain namespace.'=>'这与 Agnosis 艺术家子域名冲突——两个插件都会声明同一个子域名命名空间。','Artist subdomain routing is'=>'艺术家子域名路由','completely inactive'=>'完全未启用','until this is resolved.'=>'直到此问题解决。','Fix: open'=>'修复：打开','Settings'=>'设置','Language Router'=>'语言路由器','and switch the URL strategy to'=>'并将 URL 策略切换为','Path prefix (subfolder)'=>'路径前缀（子文件夹）','This is the LinguaForge default and allows artist subdomains to coexist with language subfolders'=>'这是 LinguaForge 的默认设置，并允许艺术家子域名与语言子文件夹共存','Agnosis — Artist Subdomain Routing is disabled'=>'Agnosis — 艺术家子域名路由已禁用','Open LinguaForge Settings'=>'打开 LinguaForge 设置','Agnosis Artist'=>'Agnosis 艺术家','My Submissions'=>'我的提交','Join'=>'加入','Send new artwork to be published.'=>'发送新的作品以发布。','Update your artist biography.'=>'更新您的艺术家简介。','Announce an upcoming event.'=>'发布即将举行的活动公告。','Replace'=>'替换','Send a new version of an existing artwork — subject must match its title.'=>'发送现有作品的新版本——主题必须与其标题匹配。','Request an existing artwork or event be taken down — subject must match its title.'=>'请求下架现有作品或活动——主题必须与其标题匹配。','Promote'=>'推广','Choose which artwork represents you in the shared community gallery on the main site — subject must match its title. Your own subdomain already shows everything you\'ve published.'=>'选择哪件作品代表您在主站点的共享社区画廊中展示——主题必须与其标题匹配。您的个人子域名已展示您发布的全部内容。','Photo-only'=>'仅照片','Publish a photo exactly as sent — no AI enhancement, no quality check.'=>'按原样发布照片——不进行 AI 增强，不做质量检查。','Pure'=>'纯净','Publish exactly as sent — no AI at all, not even the title/description pass.'=>'按原样精确发布——完全不使用 AI，甚至不进行标题/描述处理。','Send a message to every other artist in the community.'=>'向社区中的其他所有艺术家发送消息。','Spotted something to fix after publishing? Log in and look for the pencil icon on your published page — you can correct the title, text, or photo yourself, no need to email us again.'=>'发布后发现需要修正的地方？登录后在已发布页面查找铅笔图标——您可以自行更正标题、文本或照片，无需再次给我们发邮件。','Manage notification preferences: %s'=>'管理通知偏好：%s','Manage notification preferences'=>'管理通知偏好','Agnosis Membership Application'=>'Agnosis 会员申请','Agnosis Governance Participation'=>'Agnosis 治理参与','Agnosis Newsletter Subscription'=>'Agnosis 新闻通讯订阅','Agnosis Newsletter Delivery History'=>'Agnosis 新闻通讯发送历史','Agnosis Contact Messages Sent'=>'Agnosis 联系消息已发送','Agnosis Transactions'=>'Agnosis 交易','Agnosis Notification Preferences'=>'Agnosis 通知偏好','Display name'=>'显示名称','Application statement'=>'申请陈述','Language'=>'语言','Applied at'=>'申请于','Resolved at'=>'解决于','Type'=>'类型','Community vouch given'=>'社区担保已提供','Date'=>'日期','Admission vouch given'=>'入会担保已提供','Community removal vote'=>'社区移除投票','Vote'=>'投票','Community size-cap vote'=>'社区规模上限投票','Locale'=>'区域设置','Subscribed at'=>'订阅于','Confirmed at'=>'确认于','Unsubscribed at'=>'取消订阅于','Issue'=>'问题','Recipient type'=>'收件人类型','Queued at'=>'排队于','Sent to artist'=>'已发送给艺术家','Translated message'=>'翻译后的消息','Rejection reason'=>'拒绝原因','IP address'=>'IP 地址','Sent at'=>'发送于','Amount'=>'金额','Currency'=>'货币','Fee'=>'费用','Gateway'=>'网关','Your membership application/account is still active. To remove this data, use the "leave the network" link from any Agnosis email, or ask an administrator.'=>'您的会员申请/账户仍然处于激活状态。要移除此数据，请使用 Agnosis 任意电子邮件中的“离开网络”链接，或联系管理员。','Your biography, statement, and portfolio link were erased. Your email address was kept on file — your account is currently banned, and it\'s the only way this site can continue to enforce that.'=>'您的个人简介、陈述和作品集链接已被删除。您的电子邮件地址已保留在记录中——您的账户目前已被封禁，而这是本网站继续执行该封禁的唯一方式。','[message removed]'=>'[消息已移除]','Vouch messages you wrote were redacted. Governance votes you cast were kept as-is — a vote is a community record, not personal data, and removing it would silently change a settled decision.'=>'您写的担保消息已被删除。您投出的治理投票保持原样——投票是一条社区记录，而不是个人数据；删除它会在不知不觉中改变已作出的决定。','Past newsletter delivery records were anonymized; per-issue delivery counts were kept for statistics.'=>'过去的新闻邮件投递记录已匿名化；每期的投递数量已保留用于统计。','Transaction (donation/sale) records were kept in full — financial records are subject to a legal retention obligation and are exempt from erasure under GDPR Art. 17(3)(b).'=>'交易（捐赠/销售）记录已完整保留——财务记录受法律保存义务约束，并依据 GDPR 第 17(3)(b) 条免于删除。','Agnosis is a federated art-publishing plugin. The following is a starting point for describing what it collects — review and adapt it to your site\'s actual configuration before publishing.'=>'Agnosis 是一个联邦化艺术发布插件。以下内容是对其收集内容的说明起点——请在发布前根据您网站的实际配置进行审阅并调整。','What personal data we collect and why'=>'我们收集哪些个人数据，以及为什么收集','When you apply to join, we store your email address, display name, biography, statement, and portfolio link to run the community vouching process. When you email us artwork, a biography, or an event, the content of that email (including your address) is stored while it is processed and reviewed. When you subscribe to our newsletter or message an artist through their contact form, we store your email address (and, for contact messages, your IP address) to deliver that message or send you future issues.'=>'当您申请加入时，我们会存储您的电子邮件地址、显示名称、个人简介、陈述和作品集链接，以运行社区担保流程。当您通过电子邮件向我们发送作品、个人简介或活动时，该电子邮件的内容（包括您的地址）会在处理和审核期间被存储。当您订阅我们的新闻邮件或通过艺术家的联系表单向其发送消息时，我们会存储您的电子邮件地址（对于联系消息，还包括您的 IP 地址），以便投递该消息或向您发送未来期刊。','Who we share it with'=>'我们与谁共享这些数据','Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI provider (OpenAI, Anthropic, or Stability AI, depending on this site\'s configuration) to help write publication text and enhance images. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the Fediverse) as part of this plugin\'s core federation feature.'=>'提交的作品描述和图片可能会发送给第三方 AI 提供商（取决于本网站的配置，可能是 OpenAI、Anthropic 或 Stability AI），以帮助撰写发布文本并增强图像。获批准的帖子也会作为本插件核心联邦功能的一部分，通过 ActivityPub（Fediverse）公开广播。','How long we retain your data'=>'我们保留您的数据多久','Retention varies by data type; see this site\'s administrator for specifics. You can request a copy of, or the erasure of, the personal data described above at any time using this site\'s standard WordPress data request tools.'=>'保留期限因数据类型而异；具体请咨询本网站管理员。您可随时使用本网站标准的 WordPress 数据请求工具，申请获取上述个人数据的副本或要求删除。','Submitted text and images may be processed by a third-party AI provider. Approved posts are published publicly and shared across the Fediverse — this cannot be fully undone later.'=>'提交的文本和图片可能会由第三方 AI 提供商处理。获批准的帖子会公开发布并在 Fediverse 中共享——这之后无法完全撤销。','Your message may be reviewed by an automated content filter before being sent to the artist.'=>'您的消息在发送给艺术家之前，可能会先经过自动内容过滤器审核。','See our %s for details.'=>'详情请参见我们的 %s。','Privacy Policy'=>'隐私政策','Too many requests. Please wait %d seconds and try again.'=>'请求过多。请等待 %d 秒后重试。','Submission limit reached. Please wait before sending again.'=>'提交次数已达上限。请稍后再发送。','Please complete the verification check and try again.'=>'请完成验证检查后重试。','Could not verify you\'re human right now. Please try again in a moment.'=>'目前无法验证您是否为真人。请稍后再试。','Verification failed. Please try again.'=>'验证失败。请重试。','Every 5 minutes'=>'每 5 分钟','IMAP credentials are not configured.'=>'IMAP 凭据未配置。','Connected successfully. %1$d message(s) in inbox, %2$d unseen.'=>'连接成功。收件箱中有 %1$d 封邮件，%2$d 封未读。','Webhook secret not configured.'=>'Webhook 密钥未配置。','Invalid or missing webhook signature.'=>'Webhook 签名无效或缺失。','Webhook request timestamp is missing, malformed, or too old.'=>'Webhook 请求时间戳缺失、格式错误或已过旧。','This webhook request has already been processed.'=>'此 webhook 请求已经处理过。','OpenSSL is required for HTTP Signature verification.'=>'验证 HTTP 签名需要 OpenSSL。','Signature header is required.'=>'需要签名头。','Signature header is missing required fields (keyId, headers, signature).'=>'签名头缺少必需字段（keyId、headers、signature）。','Request date is too old or too far in the future.'=>'请求日期过旧或过于超前。','Signature value is not valid base64.'=>'签名值不是有效的 base64。','HTTP Signature verification failed.'=>'HTTP 签名验证失败。','Digest header does not match the request body.'=>'Digest 头与请求正文不匹配。','keyId in Signature header is not a valid URL.'=>'Signature 头中的 keyId 不是有效的 URL。','Failed to fetch actor document.'=>'获取 actor 文档失败。','Actor document returned a non-200 response.'=>'Actor 文档返回了非 200 响应。','Actor document does not contain a publicKey.publicKeyPem field.'=>'Actor 文档不包含 publicKey.publicKeyPem 字段。','Node URL is required.'=>'需要 Node URL。','Contact %s'=>'联系 %s','Contact this artist'=>'联系此艺术家','Get in touch with %s'=>'联系 %s','Get in touch'=>'取得联系','This newsletter issue could not be found.'=>'找不到此简报期刊。','Issue not found'=>'未找到期刊','Newsletter archive'=>'简报归档','Past issues of the %s newsletter.'=>'%s 简报的往期内容。','No issues have gone out yet — check back soon.'=>'还没有发布任何期刊——请稍后再来查看。','← Newer'=>'← 更新的','Older →'=>'更早 →','Newsletter archive — %s'=>'简报归档 — %s','%1$s Newsletter — %2$s'=>'%1$s 简报 — %2$s','%s Newsletter'=>'%s 简报','Nothing new to report this time — but the community is still here, and the next issue will have more.'=>'这次没有新的动态要报告——但社区仍然在这里，下一期会有更多内容。','New artwork'=>'新作品','Upcoming events'=>'即将举行的活动','%d new artwork published'=>'发布了 %d 个新作品','%d new event announced'=>'宣布了 %d 个新活动','Welcome to our newest member: %s'=>'欢迎我们最新的成员：%s','%d community vote is open — check your email for your personal voting link.'=>'有 %d 个社区投票正在进行中——请查看你的电子邮件，获取个人投票链接。','Recent work from the community'=>'来自社区的最新作品','…and %d more.'=>'……以及另外 %d 个。','Community Newsletter'=>'社区简报','Having trouble viewing this email?'=>'查看这封邮件有问题吗？','View it online.'=>'在线查看。','Unsubscribe'=>'取消订阅','Subscribe to get these by email'=>'订阅以通过电子邮件接收这些内容','[%s] Community newsletter'=>'[%s] 社区简报','[%s] Newsletter'=>'[%s] 简报','Get new artworks, artist admissions, and community updates in your inbox.'=>'在你的收件箱中获取新作品、艺术家入驻和社区更新。','Subscribe to the newsletter'=>'订阅通讯','Unknown newsletter type.'=>'未知的通讯类型。','A previous issue is still sending — please wait for it to finish.'=>'上一期仍在发送中——请等待其完成。','Please enter a valid email address to send the test to.'=>'请输入有效的电子邮件地址以发送测试。','This is a TEST send — it previews the next issue using the current draft intro and recent activity. It was not counted as a real send and no subscribers were emailed. The unsubscribe link below is a non-functional placeholder.'=>'这是一封测试发送——它会使用当前草稿导语和最近活动预览下一期内容。它不计为真实发送，也没有向任何订阅者发送邮件。下面的退订链接只是一个不可用的占位符。','The %1$s at %2$s is due to send in about a day. Agnosis drafted an intro from what\'s new since the last issue:'=>'%2$s 上的 %1$s 将在大约一天后发送。Agnosis 根据自上一期以来的新内容起草了一段导语：','It\'s already saved and will be used as-is if you don\'t act — review it, rewrite it, or clear it back to blank here:'=>'它已经保存好，如果你不做处理，就会按原样使用——请在此处查看、重写，或清空回空白：','%1$s intro drafted for %2$s — review before it sends'=>'已为 %2$s 起草 %1$s 导语——发送前请检查','Subscribe'=>'订阅','See past issues'=>'查看往期内容','Almost there — check your inbox for a confirmation link.'=>'快完成了——请查看你的收件箱，寻找确认链接。','[%s] Confirm your newsletter subscription'=>'[%s] 确认你的通讯订阅','Thanks for signing up! Confirm your email address to start receiving the newsletter.'=>'感谢你的注册！请确认你的电子邮件地址，以开始接收通讯。','Confirm subscription'=>'确认订阅','If you didn\'t request this, simply ignore this email — you will not be subscribed.'=>'如果这不是你发起的请求，只需忽略这封邮件——你不会被订阅。','Artists are automatically subscribed — there is nothing to confirm.'=>'艺术家会自动订阅——无需确认。','Subscription confirmed'=>'订阅已确认','You\'re all set — the newsletter will land in your inbox from now on.'=>'一切就绪——从现在起，通讯将会发送到你的收件箱。','Unsubscribed'=>'已退订','You will no longer receive the newsletter. Sorry to see you go.'=>'你将不再接收该通讯。很遗憾你要离开。','This unsubscribe link is invalid or has already been used.'=>'此退订链接无效或已被使用。','This unsubscribe link is invalid or has been tampered with.'=>'此退订链接无效或已被篡改。','Account not found.'=>'未找到账户。','You will no longer receive the artist newsletter. You can re-subscribe any time from your submissions page.'=>'你将不再接收艺术家通讯。你可随时从你的提交页面重新订阅。','Confirm your subscription?'=>'确认订阅？','You\'ll start receiving the newsletter once you confirm below.'=>'在你下方确认后，你将开始接收通讯。','Unsubscribe from the newsletter?'=>'退订通讯？','You will stop receiving the newsletter once you confirm below.'=>'在你下方确认后，你将停止接收通讯。','Confirm unsubscribe'=>'确认退订','That doesn\'t look like a valid web address.'=>'看起来这不是一个有效的网址。','This site isn\'t on this Agnosis node\'s list of trusted platforms, and automatic link review is turned off here.'=>'此站点不在此 Agnosis 节点的受信任平台列表中，并且此处已关闭自动链接审核。','This node couldn\'t safely load that page to review it (it may be unreachable, or blocked for security reasons).'=>'此节点无法安全加载该页面以供审核（它可能无法访问，或因安全原因被阻止）。','Automatic review of that page\'s content was inconclusive.'=>'对该页面内容的自动审核尚无定论。','Automatic review found that page\'s content isn\'t allowed to be embedded on this site.'=>'自动审核发现该页面内容不允许嵌入到此网站。','Gallery overview'=>'画廊概览','Feature this artwork in the gallery overview'=>'将此作品设为画廊概览重点展示','Featured artworks are always chosen first when selecting one work per artist for the homepage overview.'=>'在为主页概览选择每位艺术家的一件作品时，重点展示的作品总会优先被选中。','[Agnosis] Confirm removal of: %s'=>'[Agnosis] 确认移除：%s','[%s] We couldn\'t find that artwork or event'=>'[%s] 我们找不到那件作品或活动','[%s] Your artwork is now featured'=>'[%s] 你的作品已成为重点展示','[%s] We couldn\'t find that artwork'=>'[%s] 我们找不到那件作品','We received a removal request for "%s", but couldn\'t find an artwork or event with that exact title in your account.'=>'我们收到了针对“%s”的移除请求，但在你的账户中找不到标题完全相同的作品或活动。','We received a request to feature "%s", but couldn\'t find a published artwork with that exact title in your account.'=>'我们收到了针对“%s”的重点展示请求，但在你的账户中找不到标题完全相同的已发布作品。','Did you mean "%s"?'=>'你是指“%s”吗？','Yes, remove this instead'=>'是的，改为移除此项','Or simply resend your original email with that exact title.'=>'或者只需重新发送你原来的邮件，并使用完全相同的标题。','Resend your original email with that exact title.'=>'使用完全相同的标题重新发送你原来的邮件。','Your current titles:'=>'你当前的标题：','Titles are matched exactly, so a small difference in wording is enough to miss — double-check spelling, capitalization, and punctuation against the list above before resending.'=>'标题匹配是完全一致的，因此措辞上的细微差别也足以导致匹配失败——在重新发送前，请根据上方列表仔细检查拼写、大小写和标点。','"%s" is now your featured artwork on the gallery overview.'=>'“%s”现已成为画廊概览中的重点展示作品。','Any previously featured artwork has been unfeatured automatically — only one piece is featured at a time.'=>'之前被推荐展示的任何作品都会自动取消推荐——同一时间只会展示一件作品。','[Agnosis] Your submission is ready to review: %s'=>'[Agnosis] 你的投稿已可供审核：%s','event'=>'活动','artwork'=>'作品','We received a removal request for the following %s:'=>'我们收到了以下%s的移除请求：','If you want to permanently remove this %s, click the button below. This action cannot be undone.'=>'如果你想永久移除这个%s，请点击下面的按钮。此操作无法撤销。','Yes, remove this %s'=>'是的，移除这个%s','If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — your %s will remain published.'=>'如果这不是你提出的移除请求，请直接忽略这封邮件——你的%s仍会保持发布。','This confirmation link expires in 7 days.'=>'此确认链接在 7 天后失效。','📷 Photo enhanced automatically'=>'📷 照片已自动增强','We detected some photographic issues and applied AI correction to improve visibility of your artwork:'=>'我们检测到一些照片问题，并已应用 AI 校正以提升你的作品可见度：','The artwork itself has not been altered — only the photograph quality was corrected.'=>'作品本身没有被修改——仅校正了照片质量。','📷 Photo quality score: %d/10'=>'📷 照片质量评分：%d/10','Double-check the link is correct — you can fix or remove it in the form below before publishing.'=>'请再次确认链接是否正确——在发布前，你可以在下面的表单中修复或移除它。','If the link was correct, its destination may simply not be from a source this site automatically embeds.'=>'如果链接正确，那么它的目标内容可能只是并非此站点会自动嵌入的来源。','🔗 A link was not included'=>'🔗 未包含链接','The following couldn\'t be automatically embedded, so they were left out:'=>'以下内容无法自动嵌入，因此已被省略：','Its subject line didn\'t exactly match one of your existing titles. If you meant to update an existing event, "%s", resend your email with that exact title instead.'=>'其邮件主题与现有标题中的某一个并未完全匹配。如果你想更新已有活动“%s”，请改用该完全相同的标题重新发送邮件。','Its subject line didn\'t exactly match one of your existing titles. If you meant to replace an existing artwork, "%s", resend your email with that exact title instead.'=>'其邮件主题与现有标题中的某一个并未完全匹配。如果你想替换已有作品“%s”，请改用该完全相同的标题重新发送邮件。','📄 This was published as a new post'=>'📄 这已作为新文章发布','Your submission has been processed. Here\'s what our AI curator came up with — take a look and let us know if it\'s ready to publish.'=>'你的投稿已处理完毕。以下是我们的 AI 策展人整理的内容——请查看，并告诉我们是否可以发布。','On the site: %s'=>'站点中：%s','In your language: %s'=>'你的语言：%s','Looks great — Publish it'=>'看起来不错——发布它','Discard'=>'舍弃','Want to tweak the title, text or tags before publishing?'=>'想在发布前微调标题、正文或标签吗？','Open your submissions page →'=>'打开你的投稿页面 →','The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d day. Your submission stays as a draft until you decide.'=>'上面的“发布”和“舍弃”链接将在 %d 天后失效。在你决定之前，你的投稿会一直作为草稿保留。','[%s] We couldn\'t process your submission'=>'[%s] 我们无法处理你的投稿','[%s] We couldn\'t find a photo in your email'=>'[%s] 我们在你的邮件中找不到照片','We received your email, but couldn\'t process a usable photo, audio, or video file from it — so nothing was published. This can happen when an image is pasted or inserted inline rather than added as a proper attachment, or when a file arrives in a format this server can\'t convert (for example, an iPhone photo saved in HEIC/HEIF format).'=>'我们已收到你的邮件，但无法从中处理出可用的照片、音频或视频文件，因此没有发布任何内容。出现这种情况，可能是因为图片是粘贴或内嵌到邮件正文中的，而不是作为正常附件添加；也可能是文件采用了此服务器无法转换的格式（例如，iPhone 照片保存为 HEIC/HEIF 格式）。','To resend correctly:'=>'要正确重新发送：','Use your mail app\'s "Attach file" (usually a paperclip icon) rather than "Insert photo" or pasting the image directly into the message body.'=>'请使用邮件应用里的“添加附件”（通常是回形针图标），而不是“插入照片”或直接把图片粘贴到邮件正文中。','If your photo was taken on an iPhone, try switching Settings → Camera → Formats to "Most Compatible" before taking or sending it, or use "Options" in Mail to send it as a JPEG.'=>'如果你的照片是在 iPhone 上拍摄的，试着在“设置 → 相机 → 格式”中切换为“最兼容”，再拍摄或发送；或者在邮件里用“选项”将其作为 JPEG 发送。','Supported formats: JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, TIFF, or HEIC/HEIF for images; MP3, WAV, M4A, OGG, or FLAC for audio; MP4, MOV, AVI, WebM, OGG, or MPEG for video.'=>'支持的格式：图片支持 JPEG、PNG、WebP、GIF、TIFF 或 HEIC/HEIF；音频支持 MP3、WAV、M4A、OGG 或 FLAC；视频支持 MP4、MOV、AVI、WebM、OGG 或 MPEG。','Once it\'s properly attached, just send it to the same address again — we\'ll pick it up automatically.'=>'一旦正确附加，只需再次发送到同一地址——我们会自动获取它。','The photo is too dark to show your artwork clearly. Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.'=>'照片太暗，无法清楚显示你的作品。试着在白天靠近大窗户拍摄，或者用柔和的灯光从侧面照向作品。','The photo is underexposed (too dark). Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.'=>'照片曝光不足（太暗）。试着在白天靠近大窗户拍摄，或者用柔和的灯光从侧面照向作品。','The photo is overexposed (too bright / washed out). Avoid direct sunlight or flash pointed straight at the artwork — diffuse or indirect light works best.'=>'照片曝光过度（太亮/发白）。避免直射阳光或直接照向作品的闪光灯——漫射光或间接光效果最好。','The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — diffuse light or shade gives more even tones.'=>'照片太亮或发白。避免直射阳光或闪光灯——漫射光或阴影能带来更均匀的色调。','There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the surface.'=>'作品上有眩光或明亮反射。稍微倾斜画布，或改变拍摄角度，以消除表面反光。','There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or change your angle to eliminate it.'=>'作品表面有反射。稍微倾斜画布，或改变拍摄角度，以消除它。','The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus locks on it.'=>'图像模糊。请把手机或相机放在稳定的表面上，使用自拍定时，并确保作品占满画面的大部分，这样自动对焦才能锁定它。','The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still.'=>'图像失焦了。拍摄前请在手机屏幕上点按作品，确保自动对焦锁定它，并保持相机稳定。','There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake.'=>'出现了运动模糊。请尽量保持相机稳定，或使用三脚架；轻按快门或使用自拍定时，以避免抖动。','Camera shake is visible. Use a tripod or rest the camera on a flat surface and use the self-timer to avoid movement when pressing the shutter.'=>'可见相机抖动。请使用三脚架，或把相机放在平面上，并使用自拍定时，避免按下快门时产生移动。','The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and make sure you\'re close enough that the artwork fills the frame.'=>'图像分辨率太低。请使用手机的最高画质设置，并确保离作品足够近，使其占满画面。','The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and fill the frame with the artwork.'=>'图像分辨率太低。请使用手机的最高画质设置，并让作品尽量填满画面。','The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting on your camera.'=>'图像出现了像素化。请靠近一些拍摄，或在相机上使用更高分辨率设置。','The photo has a strong color cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your phone\'s Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colors.'=>'照片有明显的偏色。请在中性日光下拍摄，或使用手机的自动白平衡设置以获得更准确的颜色。','The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch your phone\'s white balance to Daylight / Cloudy.'=>'照片看起来偏黄或偏暖。请在自然日光下拍摄，或者把手机白平衡切换到“日光 / 阴天”。','The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural light source or adjust your camera\'s white balance.'=>'照片带有偏冷的蓝色调。请把作品移到更温暖、更加自然的光源下，或者调整相机的白平衡。','Part of the artwork appears to be cropped out of the frame. Step back and make sure the entire work is visible before shooting.'=>'作品的一部分似乎被裁出了画面。请后退一些，并确保在拍摄前完整呈现整个作品。','The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight on, with the camera parallel to the canvas.'=>'作品是斜着拍的，造成了失真。请正对作品拍摄，并让相机与画布保持平行。','The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in front of the artwork, parallel to its surface.'=>'作品看起来有变形或倾斜。请将相机直接放在作品正前方，并与其表面保持平行。','There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface.'=>'作品的一部分被阴影遮住了。请重新调整光源位置，或移动作品，确保表面没有阴影。','We received your submission, but unfortunately the photo quality is too low for us to show your artwork clearly. We didn\'t publish it — but please don\'t be discouraged! A simple retake is usually all it takes.'=>'我们收到了你的投稿，但很遗憾，照片质量太低，无法清晰展示你的作品。我们没有发布它——不过请不要气馁！通常只需重新拍摄一次就可以了。','📷 Photo quality score: %d / 10'=>'📷 照片质量评分：%d / 10','Here\'s what our AI detected and how to fix it:'=>'以下是我们的 AI 检测到的问题，以及修复方法：','The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork clearly.'=>'整体照片质量太低，导致我们的 AI 无法清晰处理作品。','💡 Quick tips for a great artwork photo'=>'💡 拍出优秀作品照片的快速提示','Use natural light — position the artwork near a window on a cloudy day for even, soft light.'=>'使用自然光——在阴天时把作品放在窗边，获得均匀柔和的光线。','Shoot straight on — hold your phone parallel to the canvas to avoid perspective distortion.'=>'正面拍摄——让手机与画布保持平行，避免透视变形。','Fill the frame — let the artwork take up most of the shot; crop out distracting backgrounds.'=>'填满画面——让作品占据画面的大部分；裁掉分散注意力的背景。','Hold still — tap the artwork on your screen to focus, then press the shutter gently or use a self-timer.'=>'保持稳定——在屏幕上点按作品进行对焦，然后轻轻按下快门，或使用自拍定时器。','Once you have a clearer photo, just email it to the same address as before — we\'ll pick it up automatically.'=>'等你拍到更清晰的照片后，只要把它邮件发送到之前相同的地址——我们会自动收到。','Your previous submission is saved in your submissions page in case you want to review what was sent.'=>'你之前的投稿已保存在你的投稿页面中，方便你回看当时发送了什么。','View submissions →'=>'查看投稿 →','Photo'=>'照片','%s (original)'=>'%s（原作）','%s (poster frame)'=>'%s（装裱框）','Failed to insert attachment.'=>'插入附件失败。','Artwork or event not found.'=>'未找到作品或活动。','%s already removed.'=>'%s 已被移除。','Could not remove the %s. Please try again.'=>'无法移除 %s。请重试。','Your %s has been removed.'=>'你的 %s 已被移除。','A valid removal token is required.'=>'需要有效的移除令牌。','No pending removal request found for this item.'=>'未找到该项目的待处理移除请求。','The removal link has expired. Please send another removal request.'=>'移除链接已过期。请重新发送移除请求。','Invalid removal token.'=>'无效的移除令牌。','View it live'=>'在线查看','Biography published'=>'简介已发布','Your biography has been published.'=>'你的简介已发布。','Event published'=>'活动已发布','The event has been published.'=>'该活动已发布。','Artwork published'=>'作品已发布','The artwork has been published to the gallery.'=>'该作品已发布到画廊。','Submission discarded'=>'投稿已丢弃','The submission has been discarded.'=>'该投稿已被丢弃。','Biography removed'=>'简介已移除','Your biography has been removed.'=>'你的简介已被移除。','Event removed'=>'活动已移除','The event has been removed.'=>'该活动已被移除。','Artwork removed'=>'作品已移除','Your artwork has been removed from the gallery.'=>'你的作品已从画廊中移除。','This link may have already been used or may have expired. Please log in to manage your submissions.'=>'此链接可能已被使用或已过期。请登录以管理你的投稿。','Title and full text cannot be empty. Fill them back in, or use "Discard" from the original email instead.'=>'标题和全文不能为空。请重新填写，或者改用原始邮件中的“Discard（丢弃）”。','The full text cannot be empty. Fill it back in, or use "Discard" from the original email instead.'=>'全文不能为空。请重新填写，或者改用原始邮件中的“Discard（丢弃）”。','Portfolio link'=>'作品集链接','Social link %d (optional)'=>'社交链接 %d（可选）','Hour'=>'小时','Location'=>'地点','Address'=>'地址','Timezone'=>'时区','Other'=>'其他','— Not set —'=>'— 未设置 —','Discard this submission?'=>'要丢弃此提交吗？','This will permanently discard the submission — it will not be published.'=>'这将永久丢弃该提交——它不会被发布。','Yes, discard it'=>'是的，丢弃它','Remove this artwork?'=>'要移除此作品吗？','This will remove the published artwork from the gallery.'=>'这将把已发布的作品从画廊中移除。','Yes, remove it'=>'是的，移除它','Title'=>'标题','Short description'=>'简短描述','Full text'=>'全文','Publish this %s?'=>'发布这个%s吗？','Make any final changes below, or leave everything as-is to publish exactly what was drafted.'=>'请在下方进行任何最终修改，或者保持原样，按草稿内容原样发布。','Publish it'=>'发布它','biography'=>'传记','Submission not found.'=>'未找到提交。','This submission is not awaiting review.'=>'此提交未在等待审核。','The original published item could not be found.'=>'未能找到原始已发布项目。','You do not have permission to review this submission.'=>'您没有审核此提交的权限。','Review link not found or already used.'=>'审核链接未找到或已被使用。','Invalid review token.'=>'无效的审核令牌。','This review link has expired. Please log in to manage your submissions.'=>'此审核链接已过期。请登录以管理您的提交。','No submissions awaiting review.'=>'没有待审核的提交。','Make changes'=>'进行修改','One-line description'=>'一行描述','Description'=>'描述','Tags (comma-separated)'=>'标签（逗号分隔）','Save &amp; Publish'=>'保存并发布','Publishing…'=>'正在发布…','Published ✓'=>'已发布 ✓','Something went wrong.'=>'出了点问题。','Could not connect. Please try again.'=>'无法连接。请重试。','Discard this submission? This cannot be undone.'=>'要丢弃此提交吗？这无法撤销。','Discarding…'=>'正在丢弃…','Discarded.'=>'已丢弃。','Saving and publishing…'=>'正在保存并发布…','Log in to view your submissions'=>'登录以查看您的提交','Username or email address'=>'用户名或电子邮件地址','Password'=>'密码','Log in'=>'登录','Remember me'=>'记住我','Forgot your password?'=>'忘记密码？','Book'=>'书籍','Person'=>'人物','Calendar'=>'日历','Pin'=>'图钉','Baseline (default)'=>'基线（默认）','Top'=>'顶部','Middle'=>'中间','Bottom'=>'底部','Icon settings'=>'图标设置','Biography icon'=>'简历图标','Events icon'=>'活动图标','Icon size'=>'图标大小','Icon vertical align'=>'图标垂直对齐','Icon-only links have no text baseline of their own — use this if they sit too high or low next to the artist name once Icon size is changed from the default.'=>'仅图标链接没有自己的文本基线——如果在将图标大小从默认值更改后，它们相对于艺术家姓名的位置过高或过低，可使用此项。','Icon color'=>'图标颜色','Leave unset to match the block’s own text color.'=>'留空可匹配区块自身的文本颜色。','Artist Name'=>'艺术家姓名','Envelope'=>'信封','Speech bubble'=>'对话气泡','Contact'=>'联系','Link settings'=>'链接设置','Link type'=>'链接类型','Icon'=>'图标','Biography Icon'=>'简历图标','Icon-only link to the artist’s biography.'=>'仅图标链接到艺术家的简介。','Events Icon'=>'活动图标','Icon-only link to the artist’s events archive.'=>'仅图标链接到艺术家的活动归档。','Contact Icon'=>'联系图标','Opens a popover with a form to message the artist directly. Hidden automatically if the artist has turned contact messages off.'=>'打开一个弹出层，显示一个表单以直接给艺术家发送消息。如果艺术家已关闭联系消息，此项会自动隐藏。','Artist Contact Form'=>'艺术家联系表单','Lets a visitor message the current artist subdomain’s artist. Content is rendered live on the frontend, for the artist currently being viewed.'=>'允许访客给当前艺术家子域名对应的艺术家发送消息。内容会在前端实时渲染，针对当前正在查看的艺术家。','Gallery settings'=>'图库设置','Columns'=>'列数','✦ Agnosis Gallery Overview — rendered on the server'=>'✦ Agnosis 图库概览 — 服务器端渲染','columns · proportional · random daily order'=>'列 · 按比例 · 每日随机顺序','Join Agnosis'=>'加入 Agnosis','Public application form for new artists. Submits name, email, bio, portfolio URL and a personal statement to the community for review. Content is rendered live on the frontend.'=>'面向新艺术家的公开申请表单。提交姓名、电子邮件、简介、作品集网址和个人陈述供社区审核。内容会在前端实时渲染。','Place this block on your /join/ page or in a Site Editor page template assigned to that page.'=>'将此区块放在你的 /join/ 页面，或分配给该页面的站点编辑器页面模板中。','Bell'=>'铃铛','Star'=>'星形','Lightning bolt'=>'闪电','Newsletter Popover — opens the signup form'=>'通讯订阅弹出层 — 打开注册表单','Newsletter settings'=>'通讯订阅设置','Trigger icon'=>'触发图标','Pick something that won’t blend in with icons already sitting next to it (e.g. Social Share).'=>'选择一个不会与旁边已有图标混淆的图标（例如：社交分享）。','Newsletter Signup'=>'通讯订阅','Email signup form for the public newsletter. A confirmation email is sent before anyone is added to the send list (double opt-in). Content is rendered live on the frontend.'=>'面向公开通讯的电子邮件注册表单。在任何人被加入发送列表之前，都会先发送一封确认邮件（双重确认）。内容会在前端实时渲染。','block titleArtist Breadcrumb'=>'艺术家面包屑','block descriptionSmall line identifying the artist whose subdomain is currently being viewed. Renders nothing on the main Agnosis site.'=>'标识当前正在查看其子域名的艺术家的一小行文字。在 Agnosis 主站上不显示任何内容。','block keywordartist'=>'artist','block keywordbreadcrumb'=>'breadcrumb','block keywordsubdomain'=>'subdomain','block keywordagnosis'=>'agnosis','block titleArtist Name Link'=>'艺术家姓名链接','block descriptionLinks to the current artist\'s own subdomain home. Renders nothing off an artist subdomain.'=>'链接到当前艺术家自己的子域名首页。在艺术家子域名之外不显示任何内容。','block titleBreadcrumb Icon Link'=>'面包屑图标链接','block descriptionA single icon-only link (Biography, Events, or a Contact popover) to/about the current artist. Renders nothing if there\'s nothing to show (no biography/events yet, or the artist has turned contact off), or off an artist subdomain.'=>'一个仅含图标的单一链接（个人简介、活动，或联系弹出层），指向/关于当前艺术家。如果没有可显示的内容（尚无个人简介/活动，或艺术家已关闭联系），或者位于艺术家子域名下，则不显示任何内容。','block keywordbiography'=>'个人简介','block keywordevents'=>'活动','block keywordcontact'=>'联系','block keywordicon'=>'图标','block titleArtist Contact Form'=>'艺术家联系表单','block descriptionContact form letting a visitor message the current artist subdomain\'s artist. Submits to a per-artist REST endpoint; the message is moderated, translated into the artist\'s own language, and emailed to them.'=>'允许访客向当前艺术家子域名下的艺术家发送消息的联系表单。提交至每位艺术家对应的 REST 端点；消息会经过审核、翻译成艺术家自己的语言，并通过电子邮件发送给他们。','block keywordmessage'=>'消息','block keywordemail'=>'电子邮件','block titleAgnosis Gallery Overview'=>'Agnosis 画廊概览','block descriptionProportional, randomised artwork grid across all artists. Shows featured artworks first, respects per-artist budget, supports medium filtering and pagination.'=>'跨所有艺术家的按比例随机化作品网格。优先显示精选作品，遵循每位艺术家的预算，支持媒介筛选和分页。','block keywordgallery'=>'画廊','block keywordartwork'=>'作品','block keywordartists'=>'艺术家','block keywordoverview'=>'概览','block titleJoin Agnosis'=>'加入 Agnosis','block descriptionPublic application form for artists who want to join the Agnosis network. Submits to the admission REST endpoint. Place this on your /join/ page.'=>'面向希望加入 Agnosis 网络的艺术家的公开申请表单。提交至入驻 REST 端点。请将其放在你的 /join/ 页面上。','block keywordjoin'=>'加入','block keywordapply'=>'申请','block keywordapplication'=>'申请表','block keywordadmission'=>'入驻','block titleNewsletter Popover'=>'新闻通讯弹出层','block descriptionIcon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled (Settings → Newsletter).'=>'打开一个全屏弹出层的图标按钮，其中包含新闻通讯注册表单。自包含——可直接放入页眉或页脚模板部件中；当公共新闻通讯被禁用时不显示任何内容（设置 → 新闻通讯）。','block keywordnewsletter'=>'新闻通讯','block keywordsubscribe'=>'订阅','block keywordpopover'=>'弹出层','block keywordfooter'=>'页脚','block titleNewsletter Signup'=>'新闻通讯注册','block descriptionEmail signup form for the public newsletter (double opt-in). Submits to the newsletter subscribe REST endpoint.'=>'用于公共新闻通讯的电子邮件注册表单（双重确认）。提交至新闻通讯订阅 REST 端点。','block keywordsignup'=>'注册','block titleMy Submissions'=>'我的提交','block descriptionLists the logged-in artist\'s pending artwork submissions for review and approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor template.'=>'列出已登录艺术家待审核和批准的作品提交。请将其放在你的 /my-submissions/ 页面或 Site Editor 模板中。','block keywordsubmissions'=>'提交','block keywordreview'=>'审核']];